&lt;br&gt;
&lt;div align=&#34;center&#34; style=&#34;font-size: 12px; color: blue; font-weight: bold;&#34;&gt;
  &lt;img src=&#34;https://origin.picgo.net/2025/12/01/b87ad4672b037e77eb2ff0c9c3c16afbd6914c26e8fbad2e.md.jpg&#34;&gt;
